casebody.data:
Friday, January 24, 1992

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

91-1494. State, ex rel. Applegate, v. Weadock.

In Mandamus and Quo Warranto. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus and quo warranto. Upon consideration of relator’s application to dismiss,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective January 22, 1992.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
